You deserve the very best in apartment living and our community offers an easy and relaxed lifestyle.

Description: Perry Hall Apartments offers a most desirable way of living. Our apartments are located at the heart of Perry Hall allowing for easy access to Towson, White Marsh, Baltimore City (M&T Stadium, Camden Yards & Inner Harbor) and Harford County. Our inviting apartments offer a fine blend of amenities for your entertaining or relaxation such as: wall-to-wall carpet, individually controlled air/heat, cable, satellite and internet access. Perry Hall Apartment layouts include 1 bedroom apartments, 1 bedroom with den and a huge walk in closet, and a large 2 bedroom apartment with only two apartments per floor allowing for cross ventilation. Perry Hall Apartments is a Cat Friendly Community. Our professional staff looks forward to servicing your needs. Please note that apartments are typically available to move in 3 weeks after the date of application.

Description:
PRESENTING WHITE MARSH CONDOMIMIUM FOR RENT	
Carefree Condo living – No outside maintenance!
Southfield at White Marsh – Laurel Path Court at Southfield
Great location close to White Marsh Mall, Interstate 95 and Baltimore Beltway!
This is a move-in ready, middle floor unit with 2 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. Located in the back half of the building, the covered porch looks out on maintained lawn with trees. Unit is in excellent shape! Available immediately.
* 	Sunny, bright room off the kitchen can be used for breakfast nook, dining, sunroom or home office. 
* 	Spacious Master Bedroom has walk in closet and new windows.
* 	Both bedrooms with new wall to wall carpet. 
* 	Kitchen contains convenient breakfast bar, double sink, dishwasher, disposal, oven/range and refrigerator. Oven is new!
* 	Hide-away washer and dryer provide for convenient laundry needs. New dryer!
* 	Hardwood floors in the living room/dining area – with brand new area rug. 
* 	Comfortable and energy efficient with electric forced hot air, central air conditioning.
